            ><![CDATA[
                <h2>StoneClipboarderTool 1.1.0</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>🔥 NEW: Global Hotkeys System - System-wide keyboard shortcuts for instant clipboard access</li>
                    <li>⚡️ NEW: Quick Picker Window - Spotlight-like floating panel (Ctrl+Option+Space)</li>
                    <li>🎮 NEW: Direct Paste to Active Apps - Hotkeys automatically paste to current application</li>
                    <li>🪟 NEW: Favorites - Save often-used items for quick access</li>
                    <li>🎯 NEW: Quick Access Shortcuts - Ctrl+Option+1-0 for last items, Ctrl+Shift+1-0 for favorites</li>
                    <li>🏷️ Enhanced UI - Visual type indicators and improved file previews</li>
                    <li>⚙️ Extended Settings - Hotkey configuration and advanced preferences</li>
                    <li>📊 Better Data Models - Enhanced clipboard item management with favorites support</li>
